            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". For some reason there are people who think because an old car is visible they have the right to smash the windows, scratch the paint, or do whatever they want to it. While a lot of times when the vandals are caught ",
